     {q:"Why are political cartoons considered a valuable historical and media literacy resource?", options:["They offer insight into public opinion and commentary on issues from a specific time period","These cartoons have no connection to public opinion","Political cartoons provide no historical insight","This type of media has no educational value"], answer:0}
