     {q:"Why might a country choose to fund a public broadcaster instead of relying only on private companies?", options:["Private companies always better represent a country’s identity","A public broadcaster can prioritize national content and public interest over profit alone","Public broadcasters never provide any benefit over private companies","This concept has no relevance to History"], answer:1}
